      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "This version mainly completed the internationalization of the plugin and enhanced the global search experience in Canvas.\r\n\r\n### New Features\r\n\r\n- Support for English and Simplified Chinese interfaces, with the plugin automatically switching based on Obsidian's current language.\r\n\r\n- Added a complete internationalization infrastructure covering commands, menus, settings pages, modals, notifications, toolbars, and workbench text.\r\n\r\n- Added match preview in global search, allowing quick viewing of hit context in a floating panel.\r\n\r\n- Added highlighting and positioning capabilities in global search, making it easy to jump to matched content in Canvas.\r\n\r\n### Improvements\r\n\r\n- Completed multilingual adaptation for interfaces such as settings pages, splitting, markers, properties, sorting, and merge workbench.\r\n\r\n- Optimized the text and interaction performance of the Canvas selection toolbar and find/replace toolbar.\r\n\r\n- Updated the README and technical documentation, supplementing internationalization and feature descriptions.\r\n\r\n- Updated the plugin description to more accurately cover the current feature scope.\r\n\r\n### Fixes\r\n\r\n- Fixed the issue where Group titles and connection labels would scale with the canvas.\r\n\r\n- Fixed several text, settings, and interface detail issues discovered during the internationalization process.\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/woxin667/Canvas-Loom/compare/1.7.0...1.7.1",
